{"tid":2270760,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分享blue nile買鑽石經驗","createTime":"2020-11-04T07:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T16:09:20.000Z","uid":383122,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"81c4ccc5eae3613290b5350e10ad7cc805b2ad0f","tid":2270760,"uid":383122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"之前做咗CR-ROM 好耐, 都見身邊同網上好多朋友諗緊好唔好上網買鑽石, 而家開個account 同大家分享下過程同埋利弊, 當中一啲心得等等。<br />\n我個人on and off 研究/觀察咗鑽石大概一年, 亦都親身去睇過鑽石/鑽戒, 最後就揀咗Blue Nile。<br />\n我只係買咗裸鑽,因為想番黎再揀design。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>網上購買 - 利: </strong><br />\n1. 比香港門店 (樓上鋪 如love bird) 再平 2成左右<br />\n2. 選擇較多, 一般香港小店樓上鋪我見都係入VS - SI grade, 同埋fluorescence (瑩光反應) none<br />\n3. 冇sales 嘈住俾壓力你, 但前題你要熟鑽石, 如4C , fluorescence, GIA 個commentary 等等 <br />\n<strong>網上購買 - 弊</strong><br />\n1. 冇得親眼睇石, 雖然主流網上鑽石分銷商. 有高清 360 度放大圖, 但一定冇親眼睇石咁安心<br />\n2. 送貨要預一個月<br />\n<br />\n<strong>流程:</strong><br />\n1. <strong>揀石</strong> - 網上Blue Nile, James Allen 都有幾好用的filter, 大部份石都有360 度放大圖<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>付款</strong> - 可用credit card 或bank wire transfer。bank wire transfer 會再有約1.5% discount。個人係用後者, blue nile 會將佢地香港區戶口資料email 俾你, 全程有customer service 解答你問題。網上面會揾到discount code 再平多少少。就係咁我十幾萬就過咗去。價錢包括shipping 保險。<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>等收貨</strong> - UPS 送貨, 發貨時會有tracker 知道件貨去咗邊度, 似乎係喺美國出發, 由訂貨到出貨約2-3 星期不等, 送貨地址可以係你個人地址, 或者去香港UPS 中心交收, 我揀咗荔枝角UPS 中心收貨<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>收貨</strong> - 簽名, 對身份證。個package都幾大舊, 但入面其實只係得粒石同埋GIA 證書, 喺呢個stage 你係冇辦法對你粒石係咪GIA 證書上面嗰粒。但係so far 似乎冇聽過Blue nile 有出錯/昆客。我件貨就 HK$ 147k 2.07ct, G VVS1, 3EX SB, 下面有GIA cert。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wg6XVif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWg6XVif.jpg&h=0fdfceca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. <strong>check 貨</strong> - 呢個要揾鋪頭幫你睇, 我個人就喺整托間鋪頭check 埋, 佢地鑲鑽都會check 清楚你GIA 上面粒石對唔對個證書number, 喺粒石個girdle 上面會有GIA鐳射刻印, 鑲完之後都會咁樣check 一次<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5D554bB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5D554bB.jpg&h=aa7d8d86&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7UDO1Yh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7UDO1Yh.jpg&h=a31b1a4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. <strong>上托, 求婚, 做老襯</strong><br />\n<br />\n個人心得: <br />\n1. 冇360 度圖唔揀, 因為佢個圖都算幾可靠, 如果低Clarity 如SI, 佢放大之後都幾清楚見到啲睱疵。你亦都可以幾清楚比較到每個color 的分別。<br />\n2. 上網買個人唔會揀SI, 甚至VS2 的石, 因為SI1 SI2 睱疵可以好大分別, cloud, 同睱疵的位置極影響閃唔閃。揀高clarity 確保佢唔會有啲大cloud/ 明顯睱疵<br />\n3. 好多人會話瑩光反應粒石會奶, 其實網上睇意見都幾不一, 呢個係我研究咗最耐的factor 。最後覺得影響不大揀咗strong blue, 因為比起none 平一大截, focus 番4 個C。最後收貨同其他鑽石比較都睇唔出有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n利申: 不是sales, 亦唔係賣廣告"},{"pid":"819d52e22c3917635b322c8af574ff5f93aa3b76","tid":2270760,"uid":1069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名，打算blue nile 買粒一卡，諗緊好唔好買埋個托，唔洗出面搵人鑲"},{"pid":"a214ee7c92adbd283a7689412e658a681951759a","tid":2270760,"uid":356857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"最後一張圖，mon 上面既氣泡係部儀器定粒石？<br />\n<br />\n另外請教下睇360放大圖點睇倒有冇milky? thx"},{"pid":"f245f9e1d6c60440bd0e95a034da5e2210bbd825","tid":2270760,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"血鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873e6abc93ca6b61d2da95a7f18097c407eedb36","tid":2270760,"uid":383122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a214ee7c92adbd283a7689412e658a681951759a","tid":2270760,"uid":356857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"最後一張圖，mon 上面既氣泡係部儀器定粒石？<br />\n<br />\n另外請教下睇360放大圖點睇倒有冇milky? thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"應該係粒石上面嘅塵/ 輕微打磨問題，部機放大咗50-100 倍我估，VVS1 見到花都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://beyond4cs.com/grading/other-comments/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeyond4cs.com%2Fgrading%2Fother-comments%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7e8ff071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://beyond4cs.com/grading/other-comments/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文章喺milky/ cloud 上面都解釋得幾好，你可以試下sort 啲cloudy 嘅石一齊360度睇去比較<br />\n<br />\n證書上如果佢係SI, 但係個暇疵嘅map 又好clean 要特別注意。因為可能係有cloud 佢跟本畫唔到上幅圖，所以個人建議唔好揀SI"},{"pid":"47914b25c47176ee8c9d85387fc5e70d6f8c0b53","tid":2270760,"uid":356857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"873e6abc93ca6b61d2da95a7f18097c407eedb36","tid":2270760,"uid":383122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a214ee7c92adbd283a7689412e658a681951759a","tid":2270760,"uid":356857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"最後一張圖，mon 上面既氣泡係部儀器定粒石？<br />\n<br />\n另外請教下睇360放大圖點睇倒有冇milky? thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"應該係粒石上面嘅塵/ 輕微打磨問題，部機放大咗50-100 倍我估，VVS1 見到花都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://beyond4cs.com/grading/other-comments/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeyond4cs.com%2Fgrading%2Fother-comments%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7e8ff071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://beyond4cs.com/grading/other-comments/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文章喺milky/ cloud 上面都解釋得幾好，你可以試下sort 啲cloudy 嘅石一齊360度睇去比較<br />\n<br />\n證書上如果佢係SI, 但係個暇疵嘅map 又好clean 要特別注意。因為可能係有cloud 佢跟本畫唔到上幅圖，所以個人建議唔好揀SI"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"我target vvs2, 係擔心過到嚟先發現唔閃啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2b49a4d156c93b87d8f6f4b7362c06f313bd84","tid":2270760,"uid":383122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47914b25c47176ee8c9d85387fc5e70d6f8c0b53","tid":2270760,"uid":356857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"873e6abc93ca6b61